"Old Houses on Monkey Hill"
William and Duane Streets

Pelletreau, William S.
Early New York houses with historical - genealogical notes.
New York: Francis P. Harper, 1900.

The Brace Memorial Newsboy's Lodging House, 242-244 William Street, east side, from and including Duane, Streets. The view also shows New Chambers Street, south side, from and including William, to, but not including Pearl Streets. (New Chambers Street, is arbitrarily set to run east and west).

June 24, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.
